310
00:22:20,911 --> 00:22:23,552
That Ferris wheel seems like
it was there before.

311
00:22:27,191 --> 00:22:28,728
I wanted to ride it when I was little.

312
00:22:33,351 --> 00:22:34,391
How about we do it now?

313
00:22:35,272 --> 00:22:36,992
The line probably won't be too long.

314
00:22:41,712 --> 00:22:43,032
I came here when I was a kid.

315
00:22:45,472 --> 00:22:47,151
Has it changed much?

316
00:22:48,072 --> 00:22:49,792
Even though it's changed quite a bit,

317
00:22:52,312 --> 00:22:54,111
