344
00:26:15,952 --> 00:26:17,072
There's no one else here.

345
00:26:18,272 --> 00:26:19,591
And no one will hear us.

346
00:26:22,151 --> 00:26:23,272
Whatever you want to say,

347
00:26:24,591 --> 00:26:25,272
