348
00:26:33,351 --> 00:26:37,631
What exactly have you been through
these years?

349
00:27:13,591 --> 00:27:14,671
Your father's condition,

350
00:27:15,351 --> 00:27:16,871
like memory and cognitive impairment,

351
00:27:17,351 --> 00:27:19,191
has gotten worse than before.

352
00:27:19,591 --> 00:27:21,312
The new psychiatric symptoms,

353
00:27:21,911 --> 00:27:23,671
like hallucinations

354
00:27:23,752 --> 00:27:25,272
and aggressive behavior,

355
00:27:25,512 --> 00:27:27,552
indicate his disease has worsened.

356
00:27:27,992 --> 00:27:30,272
So, first, we'll do some standard tests.

357
00:27:30,552 --> 00:27:33,272
Then we'll schedule an MRI
as soon as possible

358
00:27:33,272 --> 00:27:34,272
to examine his brain.

359
00:27:35,831 --> 00:27:39,032
Doesn't this situation
require hospitalization?

360
00:27:40,111 --> 00:27:42,391
I need the test results
before I can diagnose.

361
00:27:42,871 --> 00:27:46,792
I think it hasn't reached the point
of requiring inpatient treatment yet.

362
00:27:47,391 --> 00:27:50,032
First, he still has self-care ability.

363
00:27:50,512 --> 00:27:51,191
Second,

364
00:27:51,952 --> 00:27:55,431
aggressive behavior occurs occasionally,

365
00:27:55,431 --> 00:27:56,631
but it's not persistent.

366
00:27:57,351 --> 00:27:59,591
Third, regarding cortical damage,

367
00:28:00,431 --> 00:28:04,831
neurological symptoms
are still relatively few at present.

368
00:28:05,431 --> 00:28:06,431
Therefore,

369
00:28:07,631 --> 00:28:09,512
hospitalization isn't very necessary.

370
00:28:10,072 --> 00:28:13,431
Besides, our hospital has limited beds.

371
00:28:13,631 --> 00:28:15,151
Generally, we encourage home care.

372
00:28:16,072 --> 00:28:16,831
After all,

373
00:28:16,831 --> 00:28:19,351
the home environment is more stable

374
00:28:19,351 --> 00:28:20,351
and pleasant.

375
00:28:20,911 --> 00:28:24,191
The care and comfort from family
are what the hospital can't provide.

376
00:28:27,671 --> 00:28:28,391
Take this.

377
00:28:44,111 --> 00:28:44,752
Master.

378
00:28:46,391 --> 00:28:47,552
Can we close this case?

379
00:28:48,752 --> 00:28:50,631
The evidence
against Pang Xinghua is solid.

380
00:28:51,191 --> 00:28:53,111
No doubts about his death either.

381
00:29:28,272 --> 00:29:29,992
I heard from the neighbors

382
00:29:30,191 --> 00:29:33,391
