by some rat poison buyers.

391
00:30:00,431 --> 00:30:01,831
But so many times?

392
00:30:02,431 --> 00:30:04,671
Could it be
that someone did it on purpose?

393
00:30:05,072 --> 00:30:06,151
We have

394
00:30:06,351 --> 00:30:07,792
