404
00:30:31,792 --> 00:30:35,391
or it causes a negative social impact.

405
00:30:40,312 --> 00:30:44,431
There are many messy incidents
because of dog ownership.

406
00:30:46,032 --> 00:30:47,792
There are those with no manners at all,

407
00:30:47,792 --> 00:30:49,792
