409
00:30:53,111 --> 00:30:56,032
I heard a child in the western suburbs
was bitten by a rabid dog days ago.

410
00:30:56,431 --> 00:30:57,391
The kid didn't survive.

411
00:31:01,671 --> 00:31:02,792
You try to soothe your wife.

412
00:31:03,312 --> 00:31:05,151
She can raise a new pet.

413
00:31:08,431 --> 00:31:09,032
Alright.

414
00:31:09,512 --> 00:31:10,671
I'll keep you updated.

415
00:31:10,792 --> 00:31:11,512
Okay.

416
00:31:11,992 --> 00:31:14,151
But I can't guarantee any results.

417
00:31:15,911 --> 00:31:16,591
I'm off.

418
00:31:17,871 --> 00:31:18,871
