Just traveling around.

450
00:33:29,272 --> 00:33:32,431
Maybe going somewhere far away.

451
00:33:33,111 --> 00:33:39,712
Actually, Pang Xinghua confessed to you
about murdering Zhan Qiuman,

452
00:33:40,232 --> 00:33:40,952
