453
00:33:42,871 --> 00:33:43,952
We checked

454
00:33:44,072 --> 00:33:46,312
Pang Xinghua's health insurance card.

455
00:33:46,871 --> 00:33:49,431
We discovered that on the day
after Zhan Qiuman was killed,

456
00:33:49,752 --> 00:33:51,992
