475
00:34:56,872 --> 00:34:58,032
I was still furious.

476
00:34:59,352 --> 00:35:03,151
Besides, I didn't know
he actually ran out of medicine.

477
00:35:07,151 --> 00:35:08,231
I've taken care of him

478
00:35:10,111 --> 00:35:11,791
