I failed to discipline him.

480
00:35:16,952 --> 00:35:18,512
I betrayed our parents' trust.

481
00:35:20,392 --> 00:35:21,671
And I feel sorry for Man.

482
00:35:23,032 --> 00:35:24,711
I'll make it up
to them in the underworld

483
00:35:26,032 --> 00:35:27,392
